OL,3,CDoctor stabbed fellow surgeon after
OL,4,Cfailed plot to set house alight, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA plastic surgeon attempted to murder
OL,8,Fa fellow doctor by stabbing him in his
OL,9,Fhome in Halam, Nottinghamshire, after
OL,10,Fa failed plot to set his house on
OL,11,Ffire, a court has heard.
OL,13,FJurors were told that consultant
OL,14,Fsurgeon Peter Brooks, a specialist in
OL,15,Fburns and plastics, "hated" Graeme
OL,16,FPerks, and cycled to his house in the
OL,17,Fearly hours of January 14 2021, before
OL,18,Fbreaking in wearing camouflage and
OL,19,Farmed with a crowbar, petrol, matches
OL,20,Fand a knife.
