OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FProsecution KC Tracy Ayling told
OL,8,FLoughborough Court Brooks doused the
OL,9,Fground floor of the property in petrol
OL,10,Fafter breaking in through a
OL,11,Fconservatory door.
OL,13,FThe 61-year-old went on trial in his
OL,14,Fabsence without legal representation
OL,15,Fcharged with two counts of attempted
OL,16,Fmurder, attempted arson with intent to
OL,17,Fendanger life, and possession of a
OL,18,Fknife in a public place.
