OL,7,FThe court heard Brooks was the subject
OL,8,Fof disciplinary proceedings at work
OL,9,Fand could have faced dismissal from
OL,10,FNottingham University Hospitals NHS
OL,11,FTrust.
OL,13,FThe jury was told Mr Perks's
OL,14,Fstatements "formed part of the
OL,15,Fevidence" in the proceedings, and
OL,16,FBrooks wanted to get him "out of the
OL,17,Fway."
OL,19,F"It is clear that the defendant hated
OL,20,FGraeme Perks."
