OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe prosecutor said the victim thought
OL,8,Fa figure was his son but then "felt a
OL,9,Fblow to his body" and put his hands to
OL,10,Fhis abdomen where it was "warm and
OL,11,Fsticky and felt something poking out".
OL,13,FMs Ayling continued: "He decided he
OL,14,Fmust have been stabbed, he did not
OL,15,Fremember anything after that. His
OL,16,Ffamily heard screaming and went
OL,17,Fdownstairs.
OL,19,F"Because of quick action and amazing
OL,20,Fsurgical skill, Graeme Perks lives."
