OL,7,FJurors were told he required three
OL,8,Foperations before he was moved to
OL,9,Fcritical care and remained in a
OL,10,Fmedically induced coma after
OL,11,Fsustaining incision wounds to his
OL,12,Fliver and pancreas.
OL,14,FLater on the morning of the attack,
OL,15,FBrooks was arrested in the hospital
OL,16,Fafter he was found asleep on a bench
OL,17,Fin a garden bleeding from his hand,
OL,18,Fthe court heard.
